msgid ""
"The procedure for Poisson MLE (PMLE) requires that the dependent "
"quantities in unfolding, e.g. gross counts of a decay curve, are Poisson-"
"distributed. As the latter are applied as net count rates for the other "
"methods, these net count rate values are converted to gross counts within"
" the program. The gross counts of a decay curve"
